originalText.text: Today is January 3, 2020.  I placed an order with this company on Dec 9, 2019.  Since December 9th, I have sent several e-mails to the company and left several voice mails on their answering machine trying to detemine the status of my order. I have not received any sort of response from them.  My credit card was immediately charged on Dec, 9th but I have not seen the product nor can I get a response from the company.  I have placed the charge on my card in dispute and hopefully will get a refund.  I DO NOT recommend this company (if, in fact, they are a real company)  I gave them one star as you apparently have to give them at least one star for the review to post.
